p.d: The Power of Stand-Up Comedy! 'Gag Concert' delivers the most up-to-date source of smile and fun in Korean society. His program first introduced the new style of comedy mixed with open concert to Korea, and it now became the prototype of Korean comedy show. Composed of many short sections, the program draws laugh and smile from viewers.
